{"tid":616530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"YouTube槍擊案　女槍手為youtuber 疑不滿影片遭審查","createTime":"2018-04-04T08:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T09:35:21.000Z","uid":188,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bc6ef76ea0de1035662babcfdcc341afff8347be","tid":616530,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:44:37.000Z","msg":"美國加州YouTube總部槍擊案，當地警方進一步公布女疑犯的身份及行兇動機，懷疑她不滿YouTube的影片審查，認為是打壓言論自由。 聖布魯諾市警方發表聲明說，槍傷三人後吞槍自盡的女槍手，是39歲伊朗裔的加州居民阿格達姆。警方指她經常在網上貼文及發放視頻，又曾在視頻批評YouTube並無為用戶提供一個公平上載影片的平台，涉嫌歧視及將她上載的內容過濾。 警方又相信，阿格達姆是隨機開槍，與三名傷者並不認識。 案中有一男兩女中槍受傷，其中36歲男傷者情況危殆，早前有報道指他可能是槍手的男朋友。"},{"pid":"7890d6349f395ede0f9bae03b8481a99d0282751","tid":616530,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:44:49.000Z","msg":"youtube 8<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0d26110fd1101b5a0a311dd4c1bc3998b06022","tid":616530,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:45:53.000Z","msg":"在視頻批評YouTube並無為用戶提供一個公平上載影片的平台，涉嫌歧視及將她上載的內容過濾。"},{"pid":"a7b80faea1e800938ee8e6280c463f353bb772e5","tid":616530,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651c15e63da0825e2e5564ce98eb932d9932933d","tid":616530,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b43621f549a4921a2ab687d98d30f08c1747ec","tid":616530,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:32:25.000Z","msg":"Nasim Aghdam"},{"pid":"8586e922360313133bbe893546de265db70faa00","tid":616530,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾utube<br />\nJ Paul 班垃圾犯guideline就冇事<br />\n普通人就demonetized stri